                    &quot;Cannot cast to HashMap&lt;&quot;+ keyClass.getSimpleName()
                    +&quot;, &quot;+ valueClass.getSimpleName() +&quot;&gt;&quot;
                    +&quot;, value &quot;+ value +&quot; is not a &quot;+ valueClass.getSimpleName()
